<section>
    <div class="container">
        <h2 id="faq-heading">FAQ</h2>

        <div class="faq">
            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary
                    >Can Call Dan handle multiple handyman jobs in one visit?</summary
                >
                <p>
                    Yes, absolutely. We encourage you to group jobs together as
                    it saves you both time and money. Call Dan is fully equipped
                    to handle several handyman tasks in one convenient visit.
                </p>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary>How do I get a quote for handyman services?</summary>
                <p>
                    Simply fill out our contact form or give us a call directly.
                    We provide free, no obligation quotes quickly, tailored to
                    your specific handyman needs.
                </p>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary
                    >Does Call Dan provide same day handyman services?</summary
                >
                <p>
                    We certainly do. If your job is urgent, contact us
                    immediately and we'll do our best to assist you with same
                    day handyman service
                </p>
            </details>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    section#faq {
        background-color: #000; /* Black background */
        padding: 3rem 1rem;
        color: #fff; /* Default text color */
    }

    section#faq .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    #faq-heading {
        font-size: 2.25rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: #ffd600; /* Yellow accent for heading */
    }

    /* FAQ items grid */
    .faq {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    /* Each accordion panel */
    .faq-item {
        border: 1px solid #949494; /* Dark grey border */
        border-radius: 6px;
        overflow: hidden;
        background-color: transparent;
    }

    /* Summary (the question) */
    .faq-item summary {
        list-style: none; /* remove default marker */
        cursor: pointer;
        padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #fff;
        user-select: none;
    }

    /* Hide the browser’s default marker */
    .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker {
        display: none;
    }

    /* Custom arrow icon */
    .faq-item summary::after {
        content: "▾"; /* down-caret */
        font-size: 2rem;
        color: #ffd600;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    /* Rotate arrow when open */
    .faq-item[open] summary::after {
        transform: rotate(180deg);
    }

    /* The answer text */
    .faq-item p {
        padding: 0 1.25rem 1rem;
        color: #ddd;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    summary {
        line-height: 165%;
    }
    section {
        background-color: var(--dark);
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        #faq-heading {
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }
        details {
            width: 75%;
        }
    }

    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
        #faq-heading {
            font-size: 3rem;
        }
    }
</style>
